article_title: Marketplace Health Insurance Funded By Tax Credits In Most States

article_metadata.description: On June 30, 2015, nearly 10 million consumers had enrolled in health insurance through the marketplaces. Most of those consumers received financial assistance in the way of a tax credit. How does your state stack up?
article_metadata.author: Kelly Phillips Erb
